<br>
That Sabok (see my forum for post about him) seems to be able to do a lot with a very varied crew. Like the other poster said my 4 wizards really act as one.... <br>
<br>
A cleric is impossible to do without (rez). And I really fell that chanters are the best pullers in the game, although many will disagree. See with Chanters really high CHA they don't get attacked if their pacify gets resisted, unlike a cleric or other class with lower cha. I can pacify (reduce agro range to one foot) most any group and just pull one mob from the group, with the 1500 Rune and the 500 Rune I can take 2000HP of damage before my 3300HP with viture even gets hit.. and the mob is off me in seconds after the first wizard hits it anyway. Plus chanter does all kinds of buffs and stuffs.<br>
<br>
So Chanter/Cleric is needed then what. Well if you want to pbaoe its 3 wiz and antoher chanter (actually better than 4 wiz) or 4 wiz.<br>
<br>
If not... well maybe 4 mages (I am thinking of doing 6 mages in EQ2.....), wizards really kill mobs fast but are very mana dependent. You might try 4 chanters and run 2 with charm and two to back up charm when it breaks huh.... Necros with unresistable DOTs and also a good pet.... humm.<br>
