<br>
Bards are the best pullers in game (post 63).  The 61 lull is outstanding and bardic charmisma is usually pretty high.  They have insta no fail fd in fading memories and are the fastest of all the characters outdoors.  They wear plate and have decent combat avoidance.<br>
<br>
But, I agree that melee are impossible to multibox for positioning's sake.  I 3 box a young bard/wizzy/cleric combo on Sullon Zek after levelinga  bard to 65 on a blue server.   The bard takes all the effort and the wizzy and cleric are hotkeyed.  It does make twisting a bit tougher and I'm not sure it would be possible in a six member group.<br>
<br>
With a six member hot box:<br>
<br>
Paladin<br>
Enchanter<br>
Wizard<br>
Wizard<br>
Mage<br>
Cleric<br>
<br>
Hotkey wizards/mage and cleric.  Slow/haste cc with chanter.  Stun with pally for better aggro than warrior, cause if you lose aggro you pretty much lose a toon.  Cleric for rez a must.<br>
<br>
JMO<br>
<br>
