<br>
Bard<br>
Beastlord<br>
Mage<br>
Wizard<br>
Necro<br>
Cleric<br>
<br>
This combo requires the least amount of maneuverability and would let you concentrate on twisting with the bard. All pet groups would be possible and BST can tank great on almost any mob you would want to 6 box (obviously not huge bosses but can tank BoT minis etc. We have a few BST on the good team that are amazing tanks. Can hold aggro great and seem to mitagate damage just fine when heavily geared and AAd.)<br>
<br>
