<!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;Dreamworld:<br>
20 mobs that give 2%/character in an hour = 40%/char or 240% AA / hour<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>Realistic:</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
12 mobs that give 2%/character in an hour = 24%/char or 144% AA / hour<br>
